Sub-Task description: "Develop and implement all missing HTML template files required by the Flask app for the CarRental web application. This includes creating templates for all nine pages  Dashboard, Vehicle Search, Vehicle Details, Booking, Insurance Options, Rental History, Reservation Management, Special Requests, and Locations. Each template must strictly follow the detailed page design and element IDs specified in the requirements document to ensure seamless integration with the backend and correct rendering without jinja2.exceptions.TemplateNotFound errors. Coordinate with Programmer 1 to confirm data passed to templates and ensure UI elements match backend data structures."
