    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="reservations-page">
    <h1>My Reservations</h1>
    <div id="reservations-list">
        {% if reservations %}
            {% for res in reservations %}
                <div class="reservation-item">
                    <p><strong>Reservation ID:</strong> {{ res.reservation_id }}</p>
                    <p><strong>Vehicle:</strong> {{ res.vehicle.make if res.vehicle else '' }} {{ res.vehicle.model if res.vehicle else '' }}</p>
                    <p><strong>Status:</strong> {{ res.status }}</p>
                    <p><strong>Special Requests:</strong> {{ res.special_requests }}</p>
                    <button id="modify-reservation-button-{{ res.reservation_id }}">Modify Reservation</button>
                    <button id="cancel-reservation-button-{{ res.reservation_id }}">Cancel Reservation</button>
                </div>
            {% endfor %}
        {% else %}
            <p>No reservations found.</p>
        {% endif %}
    </div>
    <button id="sort-by-date-button" onclick="alert('Sorting by date is not implemented yet.')">Sort by Date</button>
    <a href="{{ url_for('dashboard') }}">
        <button id="back-to-dashboard">Back to Dashboard</button>
    </a>
</div>
</body>
</html>
```

templates/special_requests.html
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Special Requests</title>
    <style>
        #requests-page {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        label {
            display: block;
            margin-top: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        input[type="checkbox"], input[type="number"], textarea, select {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 7px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        textarea {
            resize: vertical;
            height: 100px;
        }
        button {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        h1 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        #submission-message {
            margin-top: 15px;
            color: green;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="requests-page">
    <h1>Special Requests</h1>
    <form method="post" action="{{ url_for('special_requests') }}">
        <label for="select-reservation">Select Reservation:</label>
        <select id="select-reservation" name="select_reservation" required>
            <option value="">-- Select Reservation --</option>
            {% for res in reservations %}
                <option value="{{ res.reservation_id }}">{{ res.reservation_id }} - Vehicle: {{ res.vehicle_id }}</option>
            {% endfor %}
        </select>

        <label>
            <input type="checkbox" id="driver-assistance-checkbox" name="driver_assistance_checkbox" value="yes">
            Driver Assistance Request
        </label>

        <label>
            <input type="checkbox" id="gps-option-checkbox" name="gps_option_checkbox" value="yes">
            GPS Option
        </label>

        <label for="child-seat-quantity">Number of Child Seats Needed:</label>
        <input type="number" id="child-seat-quantity" name="child_seat_quantity" min="0" value="0">

        <label for="special-notes">Special Notes and Requests:</label>
        <textarea id="special-notes" name="special_notes" placeholder="Enter any special requests here..."></textarea>

        <button type="submit" id="submit-requests-button">Submit Special Requests</button>
    </form>

    {% if submitted %}
        <div id="submission-message">Your special requests have been submitted successfully.</div>
    {% endif %}
</div>
</body>
</html>
```

templates/locations.html
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Pickup and Dropoff Locations</title>
    <style>
        #locations-page {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        #locations-list {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .location-item {
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .location-item p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        button {
            padding: 7px 12px;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        label {
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        select, input[type="text"] {
            padding: 5px;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
    </style>
    <script>
        function showLocationDetails(locationId) {
            alert("Details for Location ID: " + locationId);
        }
    </script>
</head>
<body>
<div id="locations-page">
    <h1>Pickup and Dropoff Locations</h1>
    <form method="get" action="{{ url_for('locations') }}">
        <label for="hours-filter">Operating Hours:</label>
        <select id="hours-filter" name="hours_filter" onchange="this.form.submit()">
            <option value="">All</option>
            <option value="24/7" {% if hours_filter == '24/7' %}selected{% endif %}>24/7</option>
            <option value="09:00-18:00" {% if hours_filter == '09:00-18:00' %}selected{% endif %}>Business Hours</option>
            <option value="Weekend" {% if hours_filter == 'Weekend' %}selected{% endif %}>Weekend</option>
        </select>

        <label for="search-location-input">Search by City or Name:</label>
        <input type="text" id="search-location-input" name="search_location" value="{{ search_location }}" placeholder="Enter city or name">
        <button type="submit">Search</button>
    </form>

    <div id="locations-list">
        {% if locations %}
            {% for loc in locations %}
                <div class="location-item">
                    <p><strong>City:</strong> {{ loc.city }}</p>
                    <p><strong>Address:</strong> {{ loc.address }}</p>
                    <p><strong>Phone:</strong> {{ loc.phone }}</p>
                    <p><strong>Hours:</strong> {{ loc.hours }}</p>
                    <p><strong>Available Vehicles:</strong> {{ loc.available_vehicles }}</p>
                    <button id="location-detail-button-{{ loc.location_id }}" onclick="showLocationDetails('{{ loc.location_id }}')">View Location Details</button>
                </div>
            {% endfor %}
        {% else %}
            <p>No locations found.</p>
        {% endif %}
    </div>

    <a href="{{ url_for('dashboard') }}">
        <button id="back-to-dashboard">Back to Dashboard</button>
    </a>
</div>
</body>
</html>
```
